    "attributes": {
        "action": "Bring Partner and Spouse Visa Requirements in Line with BNO Visas",
        "additional_details": "This cost is \u00a3250 for 5 years and only \u00a32,000 in savings required on the BNO route. For a partner or spousal visa these costs are far higher, with up to \u00a362,500 in savings required.\r\n \r\nThe Government must amend requirements for partner and spousal visas.\r\n \r\nChildren and partners have been separated since the start of the pandemic with countless people unable to meet the harsh requirements.\r\n \r\nA fianc\u00e9 visa costs \u00a31,523, plus \u00a318,600 minimum income requirement, in addition to \u00a32,389 for Indefinite Leave to Remain down the line, this is far higher than the new BNO visa.",
        "background": "Hong Kong Citizens eligible for BNO visas have access to cheaper visas than partners and spouses of UK Citizens.",
